Each student is eager to earn a good grade through early preparation and effort.
（每位學生都渴望透過提早準備與努力來贏得好成績。）
It is evident from the evidence that the engineer found an error in the engine.
（從證據中顯而易見，工程師在引擎中發現了一個錯誤。）
We need effective and efficient ways to protect our entire environment.
（我們需要有效且高效的方法來保護我們的整個環境。）
The expensive experiment was a unique experience that helped educate the public.
（這項昂貴的實驗是一次獨特的經驗，有助於教育大眾。）
You can easily enter the room to examine the example before the examination starts.
（在考試開始前，你可以輕鬆進入房間查看範例。）
Either we find a way to escape this empty building, or else we wait for the end.
（要嘛我們想辦法逃出這棟空建築，要嘛我們就只能等待結束。）
The election results show that people expect equal rights for each citizen to exist.
（選舉結果顯示，人們期望每位公民都能享有平等的權利。）
Don't envy others; instead, encourage yourself to use your energy for something endless.
（不要嫉妒別人；相反地，要鼓勵自己將精力投入在永恆的事物上。）
It’s not easy to employ someone who doesn't even want to eat or work with energy.
（要雇用一個甚至不想吃飯或沒活力工作的人並不容易。）
Even if problems exist, a good education provides the tools to solve them effectively.
（即使問題存在，良好的教育也提供了有效解決問題的工具。）
